title: Mauricio Umansky, CEO of The Agency, COVID-19 Real Estate impact
itunes:title: Mauricio Umansky, CEO of The Agency, COVID-19 Real Estate impact
description:
Mauricio Umansky, Founder and CEO of The Agency discusses the COVID-19 impact on the real estate market and what he is doing to give back to his community. He speaks with Bloomberg's Kevin Cirilli.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
